00:14:52.526 --> 00:14:56.146
retreat and destroying all potential supply lines was enough.

00:14:57.653 --> 00:15:02.243
The result was the complete and utter destruction of the French army.

00:15:03.203 --> 00:15:09.133
Now, historians have differing views on the numbers here, but it’s estimated that

00:15:09.153 --> 00:15:16.593
anywhere from 400 to 600,000 French soldiers marched into Russia in June of 1812.

00:15:17.753 --> 00:15:19.493
