00:19:04.160 --> 00:19:09.030
and parts of it are used in parts of Belgian, Polish and Italian law.

00:19:10.500 --> 00:19:17.820
In the popular imagination, he is an inspirational character, someone who epitomises French spirit.

00:19:19.330 --> 00:19:23.920
